<h1>About me</h1>
<% content_for :secondary_content do %>
    <div id="secondaryText">
	  <h2 class="top">How I can help you</h2>
	  <p>If you haven't already, I invite you to read about the <%= link_to 'services', :controller => 'services' %> I offer. Alternatively, my background may suggest another service that I could provide to meet your needs.</p>
	  <p>If you would like to know more about what I can do for you or would like to talk with one of my referees, please <%= link_to 'contact me', :controller => 'contact' %>.</p>
	  <h2>Testimonials</h2>
		<% @testimonials.each do |testimonial| %>
		  <p><%= image_tag "start-quote.gif" %><%= h testimonial.recommendation %><%= image_tag "end-quote.gif" %></p>
		  <p class="testimonialProvider"><%= h testimonial.provider %></p>
		<% end %>	
    </div>
<% end %>
<p>
  <%= image_tag("KeithJan2012.jpg", :alt => "photo", :height => "200", :width => "188", :vspace => "5", :hspace => "30", :align => "left" ) %>Having commenced working in the industry in 1983, I have accumulated technical experience on a diverse range of platforms. My roles have covered the full life-cycle of software development. I have successfully led and contributed to teams that have delivered applications to corporate and government organisations in Australia and the United Kingdom.
</p>
<p>Read on to learn more about my professional background and what others have had to say about my work.</p>
<% @achievements.each do |achievement| %>
  <h2><%= h achievement.heading %></h2>
  <%= textilize(achievement.description) %>
<% end %>
